text:
Your present got me more pumped
than a triple-weight bench press!

I got your present! I didn't expect
it to be so fun to lift!

I totally wasn't expecting your gift.
Way to make leg day extra special!

I have no idea what I lifted to
deserve such an amazing present!

If you were trying to see who could
send the strongest gift...good play!

I thought I'd return the favor! My
awesomely shredded gut told me
this would be the right call!

It feels like I gotta flex both my
gratitude AND generosity muscles,
so... Boom! Gift!

I'm all about good sportsmanship.
Just 'cause you're my rival doesn't
mean I won't return the favor!

You went all out surprising me like
that. I don't wanna be outdone, so
I got you something too!

Your timing was actually awesome.
I already had this boxed up and
ready to send your way!
I'm sure you're gonna love it!
